These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: romance, animation
Transport: skateboard, roller
1. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Transport:skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | animation |
| Transport     | roller | skateboard  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
Food: apricot, lemon
Sport: handball, water-polo
1. Food:lemon is on the right of Sport:handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | apricot      | lemon         |
| Sport   | handball | water-polo |

 #################################
 
